         <change when="2026-02-21T15:22:29-05:00"
                 who="http://papyri.info/editor/users/ngonis">Submit - Entered text and metadata for SB XXX 17431. Although the piece was originally published as of unknown provenance, all the papyri in this group that date from this period are Oxyrhynchite. I have therefore modified the provenance, adding a question mark. It was dated to 350 or 351, because of the uncertainty about whether the heading contains a consular or a post‑consular formula. This assessment is correct, but the printed edition assumes the post‑consulate as the only possibility. I have therefore added the alternative consular dating as a PN correction. The online image connected to this piece is incorrect, and so I haven't added a link.</change>
